org.treetank.node.delegates

Class NameNodeDelegate

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.treetank.node.delegates.NameNodeDelegate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    INode, INameNode

    public class NameNodeDelegate
extends Object
implements INode, INameNode
    Delegate method for all nodes containing \"naming\"-data. That means that different fixed defined names are represented by the nodes delegating the calls of the interface INameNode to this class. Mainly, keys are stored referencing later on to the string stored in dedicated pages.
    Author:
    Sebastian Graf, University of Konstanz
